GAME : Sega GT
DATE : 19.06.03
COUNTRY/VIDEO : UK/PAL
RIP NOTES : edited the audio to fit

Sega tosses in their entry in the race-career-category, meaning that this game is all about racing. Racing to win competitions, cars, money and other prizes (such as licenses for bigger cars), buying new cars to race in, upgrading cars to race in and gaining licenses to race with. 
 
Game features : 
Build, Customize and Race your own Supercharged Speedster in the first Driving Simulator for Sega Dreamcast !

* Build original cars from scratch, over 2 million combinations are possible !
* Unique handling and performance for each car based on original  specifications
* Choose from more than 130 perfectly rendered GT sports cars 
* 3 racing modes, 22 tracks, manufacturer-sponsored cups and over 20 special event races
* Split screen 2 player head-to-head mode
* Upload scores and lap times to the internet or trade your racing machines using the VMU 